comments: AWSOME!!!! WHEN I HAD HER SHE TOOK US TO THE COURTS IN BROWARD COUNTY, WE ALL GOT TO MEET WITH HER FRIEND "HELP ME HOWARD" AT HIS OFFICE. VERY CLEAR, UNDERSTANDING, AND COOL TEACHER. HER CLASS CONSISTS OF DEFINITIONS, BRIEFING CASES, AND AN EASY MIDTERM AND FINAL. JUST PAY ATTENTION AND YOU WILL BE FINE! JUST MAKE SURE YOU READ BOOK BEFORE CLASS.

Mrs. Mullane is awsome, you have to pay really good attention to what she says because she has alot of experience in the criminal justice field..... Sometimes she gets boring but she plays along if you make a joke or two, she\'s really nice!
